gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 111, Suns 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Suns, 111-99. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander led the way for the Thunder with 35 points (13-22 FG), 7 rebounds and four assists, while Jalen Williams added 31 points (11-16 FG) in the victory. Kevin Durant tallied 28 points, nine rebounds and four assists for the Suns in the losing effort. The Thunder improve to 6-4 on the season, while the Suns fall to 4-6.
